Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只是让它移动一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟离下次审核已经没什么时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪 刚才明明还没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,geji姐 这是君岛报告No.7没错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 要下载吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今也只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,geji姐 下载…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止吧 阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢啊 阿充
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,日高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 大德学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它走路的时候总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不对劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抬脚的时候 像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有一瞬间的僵直
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是马达的齿轮不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,部长 激光炮台就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要掺和到多余的事里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多就此收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会是君岛报告的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 闭上嘴乖乖听话就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说 是君岛皇的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏 你果然知道什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请让它动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,确实会僵直一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是电力不足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,系统运转正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,神代！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,笼中鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里啊 瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏 话还没说完…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海 不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么这家伙好像出毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,停不不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,停不下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那么 去年夏天发生的暴走事件的原因是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,暴…走…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏 关掉电源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过了 但没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别松手啊 阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个卸下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去会把你也拖下水的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 阿海
