Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.12,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H6F7772&\fscy80\bord0\b1\be1\fad(200,0)\frz45.25\pos(794,356)}集\N体\N昏\N倒\N之\N谜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能遇到美沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋 阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她把脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把这双脚送给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我谢谢她…
